Ac437_IBM_EGA_8x8.ttf
----------------------
Name:     IBM EGA 8×8 (accurate/Ac437 variant)
Pack:     The Ultimate Oldschool PC Font Pack v2.2
Author:   VileR <viler@int10h.org>
Source:   https://int10h.org/oldschool-pc-fonts/
License:  Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
          https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
SHA-256:  724a72213d013b49656ca10faa641bdac7d6c06dca53ca1e1147183224f02332

This is a pixel-perfect TTF reproduction of the IBM PC EGA 8×8 BIOS ROM
font, used here as the primary UI typeface to achieve the classic DOS
tracker aesthetic. The "Ac437" prefix denotes the accurate (unmodified)
glyph reproduction in IBM Code Page 437 encoding.

Attribution requirement: include the above author credit when distributing.
